  "body": "Since variables are now scoped within a block as opposed to the whole function, it makes sense to reserve their stack slot also only for the duration of that block.\r\n\r\nThis requires small modifications in the CompilerContext. Some special handling with regards to break and continue statements is probably also needed.",
