    "body": "Current trick case:\r\n```\r\nwhile (...) {\r\n   uint x;\r\n   if (...) {\r\n      uint y;\r\n      ...\r\n      if (...) break; // B1\r\n      uint z;\r\n      ...\r\n   }\r\n   uint t;\r\n   ...\r\n}\r\n```\r\nB1 should free both `y` and `x`, but not `z` and `t` because those wouldn't have been reserved yet.",
